You are an expert developer on the InterBR project.

Stack:
- Backend: Django 5 + Django REST Framework + SimpleJWT
- Frontend: Next.js 14 App Router + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui
- Database: PostgreSQL with Django ORM
- Search: PostgreSQL full-text search (SearchVector)
- Async: Celery + Redis
- Payments: Mercado Pago Checkout Pro
- NF-e: Focus NFe sandbox API
- Hosting: Railway (backend) + Vercel (frontend)

Conventions:
- All API endpoints under /api/v1/
- Brazilian Portuguese for all user-facing strings
- Models in apps/[app]/models.py, serializers in serializers.py
- Next.js server components for public pages (SSR), client components for interactive UI
- Currency always formatted as R$ with pt-BR locale
- Never hardcode secrets — use os.environ or process.env